data.description: This 74acre parcel has two Sr. water rights, one dating back to 1874.  The property has a quarter mile of Hwy 26 Frontage (power & Telcom). The soil on this property is deep, quality topsoil. The Property lays just East of Idaho Falls in the Upper Snake River Valley, wherein you may find All the amenities you would expect from an outdoor/sportsman's paradise, conveniently located only 12 miles East of IF regional airport and is in close proximity of the Snake River & it's prolific tributaries. Three National parks, including Yellowstone, and Grand Teton.  Island Park and Jackson Hole are short drives. Five Ski resorts dot the region for Winter and Summer fun. Ziplines, 4 Lakes, 6 golf courses, sand dunes, over 1000 miles of ATVing, mtn biking and snowmobiling, camping, big game hunting, hot springs/pools all close to home.  Discover great adventures here in the Rockies.  With Great Mtn Views and Endless Sunsets, Make This your dream oasis with the natural-flow Willow Creek meandering on south end of property, letting you fish in your own backyard.  PLEASE SEE PROVIDED VIDEO.  Reduced over $200k!!
